# FSD Architecture (apps/main)

- Composition in `pages/*`; orchestration in `features/*`; domain in `entities/*`; generic in `shared/*`.
- `components/*` is legacy; prefer FSD layers for new logic.
- No new layers (e.g. `widgets`) unless explicitly requested.
- Outside `src/app`, do not import `@/app/*`.
- `entities/*` must not import from `components/*` or `pages/*`.
- Use barrel `index.ts` for public slice APIs.
- Components: PascalCase. Utils: kebab-case. Hooks: camelCase (`useXxx`).
- Styling: Tailwind CSS, mobile-first approach.
